1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
笙ｪLet me write the legend笙ｪ

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 15=

4
00:00:17,839 --> 00:00:19,839
Xiaojiu! Let her go!

5
00:00:20,280 --> 00:00:21,359
Dasheng!

6
00:00:21,839 --> 00:00:25,120
Peng Dasheng, who knew you were
such a romantic?

7
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:27,399
You saved the woman in your arms,

8
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:29,920
and now you want to save
the one in mine?

9
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,880
But you can't even save yourself.

10
00:00:34,439 --> 00:00:36,280
You can't save anyone.

11
00:00:48,799 --> 00:00:49,719
Peng Dasheng.

12
00:00:50,439 --> 00:00:51,399
Be careful.

13
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,479
Touch Xiaojiu,

14
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,799
and I'll kill you.

15
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:07,359
That's big talk.

16
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,560
Let her go!

17
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:09,239
Xiaojiu!

18
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:15,400
Peng Dasheng, hand over the soul jade.

19
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:17,480
Dasheng, don't listen to him!

20
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,280
Hand it over!

21
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,560
Gulu.

22
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:12,199
Let's see what you've got.

23
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:27,479
Master!

24
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:28,960
Master!

25
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:30,199
Master!

26
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,879
Master!

27
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,840
Where is Master?

28
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,680
Master!

29
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,159
Master!

30
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,159
Miss!

31
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,240
Kill them all.

32
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,319
Leave no survivors.

33
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,080
Yes.

34
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:36,280
Boy, you're so desperate to beat me,
you've lost control of your qi.

35
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:38,000
Once your inner force runs out,

36
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,680
you'll be a lamb to the slaughter.

37
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,520
Enough talk.

38
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,599
Dasheng!

39
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,199
Boy,

40
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,400
give up.

41
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,439
I'm not done...

42
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:15,039
Dasheng!

43
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:32,800
Miss!

44
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,600
Xiao.

45
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,959
Go. Leave me.

46
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,600
No!

47
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,399
We live together,

48
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:40,319
or we die together.

49
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:40,959
No!

50
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:41,360
Go!

51
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:46,959
This way!

52
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:47,680
Stop!

53
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:51,600
Go, miss. I'll hold them off.

54
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,879
Xiao.

55
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:57,959
Get them!

56
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:28,519
Let me go!

57
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:30,560
Let me go!

58
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,600
Dasheng!

59
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,600
Dasheng!

60
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,120
Dasheng!

61
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:53,199
Xiaojiu.

62
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,279
Dasheng!

63
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:03,120
Xiaojiu.

64
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,000
Peng Dasheng,

65
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:09,199
Master was willing to spare you,

66
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:11,800
but you chose death.

67
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,639
Now you get to watch

68
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:18,959
the woman you love
die right in front of you.

69
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:20,040
How does that feel?

70
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,560
Let her go!

71
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,000
Let her go!

72
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,720
Don't bother.

73
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:29,399
The Heavenlock Chains
seal a martial artist's meridians.

74
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:30,600
The more you struggle,

75
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,560
the deeper they bite
into your flesh and bone.

76
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,839
Stop wasting your strength.

77
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,279
Just watch

78
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:41,360
as she dies because of you.

79
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,879
Let her go!

80
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:46,160
Dasheng!

81
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:50,040
Xiaojiu!

82
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,720
Xiaojiu!

83
00:07:35,879 --> 00:07:37,199
Xiaojiu!

84
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,639
Xiaojiu!

85
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,720
Xiaojiu!

86
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,439
Please...

87
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,800
Don't hurt her.

88
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:55,879
I'll do anything.

89
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,800
Anything I want?

90
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,439
Really?

91
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:02,040
Then dig out your heart.

92
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,600
I'll have it with my wine.

93
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:22,839
Dasheng, don't!

94
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,279
Xiaojiu!

95
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:02,799
Dasheng!

96
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:43,679
Dasheng...

97
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,000
Stay alive.

98
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,440
Pull him up.

99
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,600
Peng Dasheng,

100
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:16,240
look at you.

101
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:18,879
You look like a dog.

102
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,759
Eat it.

103
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,320
Eat it.

104
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,240
Eat!

105
00:11:51,900 --> 00:11:57,740
笙ｪOne thought pulls me in, the mortal
world becomes the battlefield笙ｪ

106
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:03,980
笙ｪWho traded true love
for a body covered in scars?笙ｪ

107
00:12:06,279 --> 00:12:07,720
Are you crazy? Get up!

108
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:11,759
The Demon Sect killed both my parents.

109
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,720
Sir, you saved my life

110
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:15,440
and avenged my family.

111
00:12:15,879 --> 00:12:17,039
If you'll have me,

112
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,559
I'll stay by your side

113
00:12:18,559 --> 00:12:19,399
and serve as your maid

114
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:20,360
to repay your kindness.

115
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,360
Don't worry, Dasheng.

116
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:31,879
I'll find the best doctors in the land.

117
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:33,320
Someone will cure you.

118
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,679
Now that your enemies are dead

119
00:12:34,679 --> 00:12:35,639
and your family has been avenged.

120
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:36,799
What will you do now?

121
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,799
I'll follow you, of course.

122
00:12:40,039 --> 00:12:42,000
Wherever you go, I'll go.

123
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:50,540
笙ｪOne vow became a curse,
one dream dissolved from view笙ｪ

124
00:12:51,159 --> 00:12:53,000
You're awfully rude.

125
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,039
You look down on everyone, you mutt.

126
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:54,960
Woof, woof.

127
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:57,759
Dear,

128
00:12:58,399 --> 00:12:59,200
I was wrong.

129
00:13:02,639 --> 00:13:04,799
Xiaojiu, take the Tianji Armor.

130
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:09,480
笙ｪWhy must every lifetime
lead me back to you?笙ｪ

131
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:12,159
Besides, my heart already belongs
to someone else.

132
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:17,680
笙ｪPetals fall like snow,
while love slips out of reach笙ｪ

133
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:22,160
笙ｪYou linger in my dreams,
but never come back to me笙ｪ

134
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,799
Stay alive.

135
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:30,240
I have to live.

136
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:35,000
You're about to die,

137
00:13:35,799 --> 00:13:37,559
and you're still dreaming.

138
00:13:39,559 --> 00:13:40,360
(Dasheng,)

139
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:42,799
(my father used to say,)

140
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,919
("As long as you're alive,
there's hope.")

141
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,799
(Now I'm passing those words on to you.)

142
00:13:47,039 --> 00:13:49,519
(Peng Dasheng, stay alive.)

143
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,919
(I hope we meet again.)

144
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:56,320
(Dasheng, I ask only one thing.)

145
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:59,279
(Come back alive.)

146
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:23,759
Impossible!

147
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,879
Your inner force is completely drained.

148
00:14:25,879 --> 00:14:26,720
Impossible!

149
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,279
This is the sign of a blade
drawing on heaven's power.

150
00:15:03,519 --> 00:15:04,840
Who could wield such power?

151
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,480
Grandfather! Grandfather!

152
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,559
I asked you to do one little job.

153
00:15:08,559 --> 00:15:09,639
Why are you making such a fuss?

154
00:15:09,639 --> 00:15:11,320
Why is the sky acting so strange?

155
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:17,600
Someone's using blade intent to draw
energy from heaven and earth,

156
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:19,559
then channeling lightning
into the blade.

157
00:15:19,559 --> 00:15:20,679
Only a handful of people in this world

158
00:15:20,679 --> 00:15:22,600
could do that.

159
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:26,480
Oh no! Master's in danger.

160
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:32,080
Today, you'll die.

161
00:15:39,340 --> 00:15:39,820
笙ｪCome on笙ｪ

162
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:45,020
笙ｪThis battle, I won't retreat笙ｪ

163
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:49,940
笙ｪIn worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust笙ｪ

164
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:53,140
笙ｪAmong the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?笙ｪ

165
00:15:53,380 --> 00:15:56,220
笙ｪThey say my birth
has already decided my path笙ｪ

166
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:59,220
笙ｪBut I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth笙ｪ

167
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:02,700
笙ｪWith one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms笙ｪ

168
00:16:02,940 --> 00:16:05,940
笙ｪCovered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless笙ｪ

169
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:09,020
笙ｪIf this world only bows
to status and bloodlines笙ｪ

170
00:16:09,180 --> 00:16:11,940
笙ｪThen I'll break every rule
with a single slash笙ｪ

171
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:15,820
笙ｪListen, this heartbeat echoes笙ｪ

172
00:16:15,860 --> 00:16:18,860
笙ｪFate is nothing but a net笙ｪ

173
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:24,540
笙ｪEither be trapped by it
or tear it apart笙ｪ

174
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:26,980
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

175
00:16:27,540 --> 00:16:30,060
笙ｪI don't believe
anyone is born above another笙ｪ

176
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:33,180
笙ｪEven this mortal body
dares to fight back笙ｪ

177
00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:36,980
笙ｪI'll step on fate and grow beyond it笙ｪ

178
00:16:37,580 --> 00:16:39,700
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

179
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:42,740
笙ｪEven if the world's cold stares
stand in my way笙ｪ

180
00:16:42,900 --> 00:16:46,180
笙ｪThis blade will cut through
all worldly judgment笙ｪ

181
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:50,500
笙ｪI am my own king笙ｪ

182
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:05,140
笙ｪI emerge into the world笙ｪ

183
00:17:05,140 --> 00:17:06,900
笙ｪUnknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world笙ｪ

184
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:08,260
笙ｪMy pride is my trump card笙ｪ

185
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:10,060
笙ｪEven if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield笙ｪ

186
00:17:10,060 --> 00:17:11,460
笙ｪBorn with a gift, I won't give in笙ｪ

187
00:17:11,460 --> 00:17:13,220
笙ｪAgainst heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise笙ｪ

188
00:17:13,220 --> 00:17:14,740
笙ｪA sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain笙ｪ

189
00:17:14,740 --> 00:17:16,460
笙ｪI dare to break every rule笙ｪ

190
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:17,780
笙ｪI see through
the masks of human hearts笙ｪ

191
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:19,620
笙ｪFamous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise笙ｪ

192
00:17:19,620 --> 00:17:20,860
笙ｪThey kneel and beg for fame笙ｪ

193
00:17:20,860 --> 00:17:23,100
笙ｪI stand and fight for my dignity笙ｪ

194
00:17:23,100 --> 00:17:24,620
笙ｪFacing powerful foes, I will not bow笙ｪ

195
00:17:24,620 --> 00:17:26,220
笙ｪWith my blade in hand,
I decide what is right笙ｪ

196
00:17:26,220 --> 00:17:27,820
笙ｪStand for justice and never step back笙ｪ

197
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:29,540
笙ｪEven if the whole world
stands against me笙ｪ

198
00:17:29,540 --> 00:17:31,260
笙ｪUntamed,
frost has carved me to the bone笙ｪ

199
00:17:31,260 --> 00:17:32,620
笙ｪOnly then do I become more like myself笙ｪ

200
00:17:32,620 --> 00:17:34,260
笙ｪFight, this life of mine is unyielding笙ｪ

201
00:17:34,260 --> 00:17:35,740
笙ｪNo matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it笙ｪ

202
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:37,460
笙ｪFor love, I do not fight for the world笙ｪ

203
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:39,060
笙ｪI only want
to protect her for a lifetime笙ｪ

204
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,620
笙ｪCarefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay笙ｪ

205
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:44,940
笙ｪNow I know all things can be overcome笙ｪ

206
00:17:44,940 --> 00:17:47,100
笙ｪI raise my blade and change my fate笙ｪ

207
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:49,700
笙ｪLet me write the legend笙ｪ

208
00:17:54,580 --> 00:17:57,140
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

209
00:17:57,140 --> 00:18:00,460
笙ｪWin or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me笙ｪ

210
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:02,940
笙ｪEven if I fall, I will still shine笙ｪ

211
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:07,020
笙ｪLet my name
be carved into the vast world笙ｪ

212
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:09,980
笙ｪI rise against fate and fight笙ｪ

213
00:18:10,100 --> 00:18:12,460
笙ｪIf this world refuses to forgive me笙ｪ

214
00:18:12,460 --> 00:18:15,500
笙ｪThen I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance笙ｪ

215
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:20,540
笙ｪAnd trade it for a new dawn笙ｪ
